1721
01:28:52,051 --> 01:28:54,554
Her son had been killed
and I'd come back alive.

1722
01:28:54,554 --> 01:28:56,388
She was very bitter.

1723
01:28:56,388 --> 01:28:59,517
The first night I came home,
I got into my old bed,

1724
